tak som Nangmyun prestal jesť.

549
00:38:46,400 --> 00:38:47,640
Naozaj?

550
00:38:48,330 --> 00:38:52,290
Keby som to vedela, išli by sme tam.

551
00:38:52,950 --> 00:38:55,600
Ak by tam tá mŕtva, stará pani bola,

552
00:38:55,600 --> 00:38:58,200
